Pilates 101: 4-Week Beginner Series
Starts Tuesday May 13th at 7:30 PM

Learn like Pilates would have wanted you to! Check out the pics of him, He was FIERCE!!! This in-studio series is designed for absolute beginners or anyone looking to revisit the foundations of Classical Pilates.

What’s included:

A step-by-step breakdown of the Classical Mat repertoire
Instruction in proper breathing and alignment
A personal movement assessment to support your individual needs
$150 for the full 4-week series.
Limited spaces available. Register via the link in bio or send a direct message.
